    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h1",
          "text": "Microsoft Fabric Reporting Boosts Real Estate Operational Efficiency by 13%"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Our Microsoft Fabric experts enhanced the reporting capabilities of a real estate business, providing them with a consolidated and real-time view of their global operations through the implementation of Microsoft Fabric."
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "GAIN ACTIONABLE INSIGHTS FASTER",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Microsoft-Fabric-Reporting-Boosts-Real.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 836,
          "h": 544
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Home » Microsoft Fabric Reporting Boosts Real Estate Efficiency by 13%"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "London, UK"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Real Estate Services"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Large Enterprise"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Savills"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "Savills has been in the real estate business since 1855. They are headquartered in London, UK, along with their vast corporate spread across 700 offices in more than 70 countries situated in the Americas, Europe, Asia Pacific, Africa, and the Middle East. Their real estate services portfolio includes selling and leasing residential and commercial properties, valuation and consultancy, property and facility management, investment advisory, development services, and market research."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/savills-reb6f7dtiyiw5ofu4vsmvdys4xzyvzp2ffgjjasafk.webp",
          "alt": "savills",
          "w": 200,
          "h": 200
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Data Fragmentation & Inconsistent Reporting"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual compilation of diverse dietary preferences from numerous sources caused time delays"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Relied on manual efforts for data consolidation, eating up valuable time and hindering operational scalability"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The varying data extraction methods led to reporting inconsistencies and discrepancies"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The reports lacked operational insights, hindering strategic initiatives and decision-making"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The lack of real-time reporting missed out on taking critical business decisions on-spot for the efficient performance"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Savills struggled to establish a cohesive and optimized reporting environment. The primary goal was to aggregate and optimize data from multiple disparate data sources. These data sources comprised Microsoft Dynamics F&O and Salesforce alongside other file-based uploads within Azure Data Lake and SharePoint. This fragmentation of data resulted in:"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "OVERCOME REAL ESTATE DATA CHALLENGES",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Real Estate Data Consolidation and Reporting Using Microsoft Fabric"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 collaborated with Savills to transform their reporting landscape. We designed and implemented Microsoft Fabric, which produced a scalable reporting solution. We took two approaches, optimizing their current reporting assets and constructing a complete 360° reporting platform. The main aspects"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Strategic Optimization of Existing Reports"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Microsoft Fabric as the Core Analytics Platform"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Medallion Architecture Implementation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Automated Data Pipelines"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Data Unification & Consolidation"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "We deeply analyzed Savills’ existing reporting infrastructure to highlight bottlenecks and refine reporting logic for maximized performance and data accuracy.",
        "We established a cloud-native data analytics platform. It served as the main pillar system for data ingestion, transformation, and analysis.",
        "Implemented Medallion Architecture within MS Fabric, which consisted of Fabric Lakehouses to ingest raw data from disparate sources, then cleaning this raw data using Fabric Pipelines and Notebooks.",
        "The data pipelines within MS Fabric utilizes ETL process in ingesting data timely and efficiently along with effortless movement between Medallion layers.",
        "The meticulous schema design and transformation logic with Fabric Notebooks, we managed to unify the data, creating a central data repository and eliminating silos for holistic business performance analysis."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "EXPLORE OUR REAL ESTATE DATA SOLUTIONS",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": []
    },
