    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Business Outcomes"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Unified Data & Real-Time Insights"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Enhanced Decision-Making"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Maximized Data Value & ROI"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Business Scalability"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "The implementation of this Microsoft Copilot automation solution yielded measurable results for our client:",
        "A single, holistic, and real-time view of real estate operations saw an efficiency gain of over 13%.",
        "The improvement in report generation time and data accuracy led to informed strategic planning that made Savills join the ranks of successful real estate firms using data analytics.",
        "Accessing the full potential of Savills’ diverse data ecosystem with advanced analytics and reporting capabilities, resulting in 5-7% higher returns.",
        "An automated and flexible reporting platform provided opportunities for them to grow their real estate services across different regions without any data-related disruption."
      ],
